# 07.01 Product Overview

## Overview

The Product Overview defines the core product vision, structure, and user value of cmdOS.

cmdOS transforms the traditional relationship between humans and computers by introducing an AI-native execution layer.

Instead of users manually operating applications, cmdOS allows users to express goals and enables AI Agents to execute tasks across digital environments.

Core principle:

Human Intent

↓

AI Understanding

↓

Autonomous Planning

↓

Execution

↓

Real-World Result

---

# 1. Product Vision

The vision of cmdOS is to create the first AI Execution Operating System.

A system where users do not interact with computers through applications first.

Instead:

Users express intent.

cmdOS understands the objective.

AI creates the execution plan.

Agents perform actions.

The system returns results.

---

# 2. Product Mission

The mission of cmdOS is to simplify digital interaction by removing unnecessary technical complexity.

cmdOS aims to allow anyone to:

- Automate tasks
- Control applications
- Manage workflows
- Access digital services
- Create AI-powered processes

without requiring:

- Programming knowledge
- Complex configurations
- Manual application workflows

---

