# 4. Product Architecture

The cmdOS product consists of several major layers.

---

# User Experience Layer

## Purpose

Provides the interaction interface between users and cmdOS.

Includes:

- CMD interface
- Desktop interface
- Mobile interface
- Voice interaction
- Visual controls

---

# AI Intelligence Layer

## Purpose

Provides understanding and reasoning.

Includes:

- Intent recognition
- Context understanding
- Planning
- Decision making

---

# Agent Layer

## Purpose

Provides autonomous task execution.

Includes:

- Personal agents
- Specialized agents
- Workflow agents

---

# Capability Layer

## Purpose

Provides executable actions.

Includes:

- Applications
- APIs
- Plugins
- External services

---

# Execution Layer

## Purpose

Transforms AI decisions into real-world actions.

Includes:

- Desktop automation
- Application interaction
- System operations
- External execution

---

